Question 2: An application that doubles a value and calls one method and return a value to be displayed back to the user

start
	//Declarations of variables
	num userNumber
	num doubledTotal
	
	//Open the program
	output "Welcome to the doubled value program"
	
	//Prompt the user to enter a value
	output " Please enter a value that you want to double:"
	input userNumber
	
	//Call a method to return a total
	doubledTotal = getDoubledTotal (userNumber)
	
	//Display the total
	output "The value doubled is:"
	output doubledTotal
	
stop

num getDoubledTotal(num userNumber)
	//Declarations
	num total 
	num MULTIPLIOR = 2
	
	//Calculate the value's total
	total = userNumber * MULTIPLIOR
	
return total